# 🚀 Planetfall Protocol

The exploration cruiser **Aurora Drift** glides through deep space like a silver needle threading the stars. ✨

You are its captain — calm under pressure, curious in the face of the unknown, and responsible for every soul aboard.

For weeks, your crew has followed faint signals from an uncharted world at the edge of mapped space. The transmissions are fragmented, rhythmic, and unmistakably artificial. 📡

Some officers compare the mission to the grand expeditions of old spacefaring legends — part diplomacy, part science, part danger.

Tonight, at last, the mysterious planet fills the main viewscreen.

> [[Continue to the briefing 🧭->Planet Briefing]]


:: Village After Victory {"position":"1050,250","size":"100,100"}
--
# 🏘️ Return to the Village

When the villagers see you coming back from the cave, they fall silent.

Then the elder smiles.

“It is finished,” she says softly.

Your crew says nothing, but the truth is written across your armor, your soot-streaked faces, and the relieved rise and fall of your breathing. 🙌

The villagers thank you for ending the threat that haunted their world.

You tap your communicator and call the **Aurora Drift**.

> [[Beam up in triumph 🚀->Win Heroic]]


:: Village Warning {"position":"625,300","size":"100,100"}
visitedVillage: true
--
# 🏘️ The Village

The villagers tense when they see your landing team, but an elder steps forward and studies your uniforms.

“Travelers from the sky,” she says, “the beast in the cave can be defeated — but only if you strike when the crystal plates beneath its neck begin to glow.” ✨

She points toward the cliffs.

“Do not waste your strength on its armored hide. Watch the light. Then strike fast.”

Your crew has learned something important. 🧠

The warning confirms the best moment to attack and may be the difference between defeat and survival.

You thank the villagers and turn toward the cave.

> [[Go to the cave with the villagers' warning 🕳️->Cave Entrance]]


:: Win Heroic {"position":"1050,400","size":"100,100"}
--
# 🏆 Mission Complete

You explored the unknown, uncovered the truth, and led your team through danger to victory.

Back aboard the **Aurora Drift**, this mission will be told and retold as one of the great adventures of your command. 🚀✨

**Ending:** _Captain of Planetfall_

> {restart link, label: 'Play again 🔄'}

